{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775898620619,"sessionID":"ses_284369e59ffeHdgLjlbiaIcKCA","part":{"id":"prt_d7bce7248001haBHSXeaTjtIj1","messageID":"msg_d7bcac20d001pVLUGq4K7aYxV6","sessionID":"ses_284369e59ffeHdgLjlbiaIcKCA","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-dc0070da66224d15b980734ff3fc36cc","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-039/tasks.md","content":"# AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod) Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod) |\n| Module | pkg |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Router JWT Tests Enhancement (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Add test for `NewJWTManagerWithClient` with valid k8s client\n  - Purpose: Test JWT manager creation with Kubernetes client\n  - File: `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestNewJWTManagerWithClient ./pkg/router/`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2**: Add test for `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret` with mock k8s client\n  - Purpose: Test secret creation and loading flow\n  - File: `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestJWTManagerTryStoreOrLoad ./pkg/router/`\n\n- [ ] **T1.3**: Add test for `StoreKeysToSecret` update existing secret scenario\n  - Purpose: Test secret update flow\n  - File: `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestJWTManagerStoreKeysUpdate ./pkg/router/`\n\n- [ ] **T1.4**: Add test for `LoadKeysFromSecret` with invalid PEM data\n  - Purpose: Test error handling for malformed secret data\n  - File: `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestJWTManagerLoadKeysInvalidPEM ./pkg/router/`\n\n- [ ] **T1.5**: Add test for token validation with clock skew\n  - Purpose: Test `ValidateTokenWithSkew` method\n  - File: `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestJWTManagerValidateTokenWithSkew ./pkg/router/`\n\n- [ ] **T1.6**: Add benchmark for `RefreshToken` operation\n  - Purpose: Measure refresh token performance\n  - File: `pkg/router/jwt_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -bench=BenchmarkJWTRefreshToken ./pkg/router/`\n\n### Phase 2: Router Server Tests Enhancement (ST-2)\n\n- [ ] **T2.1**: Add test for `handleInvoke` with no entry points\n  - Purpose: Test error response when sandbox has no entry points\n  - File: `pkg/router/server_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestServerHandleInvokeNoEntryPoints ./pkg/router/`\n\n- [ ] **T2.2**: Add test for `handleInvoke` with invalid entry point path\n  - Purpose: Test routing with malformed invocation path\n  - File: `pkg/router/server_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestServerHandleInvokeInvalidPath ./pkg/router/`\n\n- [ ] **T2.3**: Add test for `handleGetSandboxError` with various error types\n  - Purpose: Test error mapping for different error categories\n  - File: `pkg/router/server_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestServerHandleGetSandboxError ./pkg/router/`\n\n- [ ] **T2.4**: Add test for server with TLS configuration\n  - Purpose: Test TLS server initialization and startup\n  - File: `pkg/router/server_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestServerTLS ./pkg/router/`\n\n- [ ] **T2.5**: Add test for concurrent request handling\n  - Purpose: Verify concurrency limit middleware behavior under load\n  - File: `pkg/router/server_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestServerConcurrentRequests ./pkg/router/`\n\n- [ ] **T2.6**: Add integration test for full request lifecycle\n  - Purpose: Test complete request flow from entry to proxy\n  - File: `pkg/router/server_test.go`\n  - Verification: `go test -v -run TestServerFullLifecycle ./pkg/router/`\n\n### Phase 3: Router Session Manager Tests Enhancement (ST-3)\n\n- [ ] **T3.1**: Add test for `createSandbox` with invalid request validation\n  - Purpose: Test CreateSandboxReq